来吴悦可以带着室友一起赚钱。并且室友一开始同意直播现在又反对，属于是背刺吴悦。 也有人说宿舍本来就是个人休息的地方，做直播肯定会影响室友，并且吴悦这样的网红在直播里谈及宿舍矛盾，粉丝说不定会去网暴室友。 想听听大家的想法，你会同意室友在宿舍直播吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f99d9866f5ee21a78e8150a87d76f9e0.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019407841107079886"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI0/7Ssd22rd1SEAMaCTExODg2Njg5MSD8o4POBjAAOKoGQBtyEzIwMTk0MDc4NDExMDcwNzk4ODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1774492005.775637", "card_id": "Q_1982441745330480829", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 84}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有没有一张照片可以展示你家猫独特魅力的照片？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "求解答"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-055db477a4691c183f95aa21e90ddc11_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1982441745330480829"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI0/7Ssd22rd1SEAMaCTExNzY3MzI3MiCgrenJBjAAOF1AHHITMTk4MjQ0MTc0NTMzMDQ4MDgyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1774492005.780077", "card_id": "Q_2019801715000436117", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在有些小孩连给书翻页都不会，需要上「翻书培训班」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "就是那种比如老师说要翻到 30 页，有的小朋友只会从第一页开始一页一页翻，有的就会乱翻，只要翻开不是 30 页就随便再翻一次 深度 | 翻书、跳绳都要上培训班，「笨小孩」怎么养成的？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dfd74e8b92fc07e8157afdbeee922458_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/